<section
  class="bg-zinc-950 py-24 lg:py-32 relative overflow-hidden border-t border-zinc-900/60"
>
  <!-- Pulsing Glowing Sphere Backdrop (resembling reference visual bottom CTA) -->
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-72 h-72 sm:w-96 sm:h-96 rounded-full border border-secondary-500/15 bg-gradient-to-br from-secondary-500/5 to-transparent blur-xl opacity-30 animate-pulse pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>
  <div
    class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 rounded-full bg-secondary-500/3 blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"
    aria-hidden="true"
  >
  </div>

  <div
    class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center reveal"
  >
    <h2
      class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-black text-white leading-tight tracking-tight font-display"
    >
      ¿Listo para dar el siguiente gran salto tecnológico?
    </h2>
    <p
      class="mt-4 text-zinc-400 text-sm sm:text-base lg:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
    >
      No dejes que la falta de un software a la medida o una web desactualizada
      frene el crecimiento de tu PYME. En Grupo Rincon estamos listos para
      ponernos la camiseta de tu equipo.
    </p>

    <div
      class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4"
    >
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/584262590251"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="glow-btn cursor-pointer inline-flex items-center gap-2.5 bg-secondary-500 hover:bg-secondary-600 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full text-sm font-bold tracking-wide transition-all duration-300"
      >
